consumption.cssSetup:
Import tokens CSS at your app entry point: import '@ds-mo/tokens/css';
This provides all var(--color-*), var(--dimension-*), var(--effect-*), and var(--typography-*) custom properties.
For dark mode, set data-theme="dark" on <html>.

